# JanShalu - E-Commerce Web Application

## Project Overview

JanShalu is a Full-Stack E-Commerce Web Application developed using PHP, MySQL, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The platform allows users to browse products, add items to a shopping cart, place orders, and track their purchases. It also includes a dedicated Admin Panel for managing products and customer orders.

---

## Features

### User Module

- User Registration
- User Login & Logout
- View Products
- Product Details Page
- Add to Cart
- Update Cart Quantity
- Remove Items from Cart
- Checkout System
- View Order History
- Cancel Orders

### Admin Module

- Admin Login
- Dashboard Overview
- Add Products
- Edit Products
- Delete Products
- Manage Customer Orders
- Update Order Status
- Monitor Store Activity

---

## Technologies Used

### Frontend
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

### Backend
- PHP

### Database
- MySQL

### Design
- Glassmorphism UI
- Responsive Layout
- Dark Lavender Theme

