---

## Installation

1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/ShaliniPrakash-907/JanShalu-Ecommerce-Web-Application.git
```

2. Move the project folder to XAMPP htdocs directory.

3. Import the database file into phpMyAdmin.

4. Configure database credentials in `db.php`.

5. Start Apache and MySQL.

6. Open the project:

```text
http://localhost/JanShalu-Ecommerce-Web-Application
```

